snippet.title: Asphalt Legends Unite - Play Together
snippet.description:
Join us and Frankie Muniz as we get ready to play together with the release of Asphalt Legends Unite on July 17th!

With our first ever expansion, you'll be able to play against your friends, no matter their choice of platform.

Players on Android, iOS, Xbox, Windows, Steam, Nintendo Switch, and PlayStation will finally be able to race together!

So what are you waiting for? Gather your friends as it'll be time to find out who the best racer is!

#asphaltlegendsunite #ALU
Play Asphalt 9: http://gmlft.co/A9YTDL

To get the latest news from Asphalt, follow us on:
Facebook Asphalt Legends Unite: https://www.facebook.com/Asphalt9Legends/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/asphalt
Instagram:https://www.instagram.com/asphaltgames
Discord: https://discord.gg/asphaltlegendsunite
